			<div class="content" id="post-content-4013154">
									

<p>This thread is intended to connect people who can Photoshop images and those people who need Photoshopped images. Feel free to offer services or ask for a picture to be Photoshopped.</p>
<p>All request posts must be made as a new reply to this thread. Provided images should be put in a collapsible or linked to in a reply to the specific request post.</p>
<p>Some rules to keep in mind when asking for images:</p>
<ol>
<li>Provide a link to a ready-to-post draft or existing article that the picture will go into. Don't make the volunteers' skills go to waste.</li>
<li>Do not demand overly complex Photoshops. This is up to your judgment, but err on the side of simplicity.</li>
<li>Do not expect your request to be fulfilled immediately - or at all. This is entirely voluntary, and there are far more people who need Photoshopped images than people who can Photoshop images.</li>
</ol>
<p>Happy Photoshopping!</p>

